{"tid":384673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【國歌法】鄺美雲：不尊重國歌即不尊重自己　照下鏡就知自己係中國人","createTime":"2017-09-02T13:35:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T02:21:10.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":132,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0797feabb6b4ced146196d88f6b5342327a4c110","tid":384673,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T13:35:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170902/s00001/870efefada2366acdf7036135a1f5229.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170902%2Fs00001%2F870efefada2366acdf7036135a1f5229.jpg&h=130bcca4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170902/s00001/1504323477561\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170902%2Fs00001%2F1504323477561&d=yMFP2zG%2F2ckRvWmh7XTl6LIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=eb410034\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170902%2Fs00001%2F1504323477561&h=7cca2919\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170902/s00001/1504323477561</a><br />\n<br />\n《國歌法》立法問題引起社會關注。藝人鄺美雲認為，應感恩自己中國人身分。<br />\n<br />\n鄺美雲接受網媒《港人講地》訪問時指出，「尊重國家等於尊重自己，你不尊重你的國歌，不尊重你的國家，你即是不尊重你自己」。她強調要知道自己根本，「你係中國人，你要唱國歌」，質疑為何要用不尊重的行為抗議，「尊重自己身分，尊重自己是中國人，你要感恩這事情」。<br />\n<br />\n鄺美雲另提到，有些人喜愛反叛，要與其他人不一樣，惟她表示「如何不一樣，你照下鏡，你是中國人，你真是一個中國人」。<br />\n<br />\n行政會議成員、新民黨主席葉劉淑儀早上出席電台節目時，呼籲市民毋須太擔心《國歌法》立法問題，強調保護國家尊嚴是「應有之義」。 問到有人憂慮會因普通話讀音不正惹來刑責，她笑言「我都係用廣東話唱，喺香港」。"},{"pid":"3c20ae4d08fb5bdc9aede665ca8698c451d1155c","tid":384673,"uid":53687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T13:40:04.000Z","msg":"無知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d2e16e3c2141b84c688b55d41722b4ae0552ff5","tid":384673,"uid":20241,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T13:41